Package com.github.blutorange.maven.plugin.closurecompiler.plugin

Class FileSet

java.lang.Object
com.github.blutorange.maven.plugin.closurecompiler.plugin.FileSet
public class FileSet extends Object
A file set consisting of includes and excludes. The includes are evaluated first, then the excludes are subtracted.
